Banco BTG Pactual SA, the Brazilian
bank led by billionaire  Andre Esteves , acquired a 30 percent
stake in Vivere Brasil Servicos & Solucoes de Credito, a company
that manages real estate loans, Valor Economico reported,
without saying where it obtained the information.  BTG declined to comment on the acquisition, according to
